bicycle-relief.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28064133/lachlan-morton-alt-tour-de-france-world-bicycle-relief-297x210.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28064133/lachlan-morton-alt-tour-de-france-world-bicycle-relief-800x565.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28064133/lachlan-morton-alt-tour-de-france-world-bicycle-relief-120x85.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28064133/lachlan-morton-alt-tour-de-france-world-bicycle-relief-768x543.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28064133/lachlan-morton-alt-tour-de-france-world-bicycle-relief-696x492.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28064133/lachlan-morton-alt-tour-de-france-world-bicycle-relief-1068x755.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28064133/lachlan-morton-alt-tour-de-france-world-bicycle-relief-594x420.jpg 594w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28064133/lachlan-morton-alt-tour-de-france-world-bicycle-relief-100x70.jpg 100w\"></a></p><p>Why? Lachlan’s Alt Tour is in aid of World Bicycle Relief. His partners, EF Education and Rapha are donating 500 bikes to the non-profit, who deliver bicycles to people all over the world who are most in need.</p><figure id=\"attachment_263138\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-263138\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28064144/lachlan-morton-world-bicycle-relief-alt-tour-solo-challenge.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28064144/lachlan-morton-world-bicycle-relief-alt-tour-solo-challenge.jpg\" alt=\"lachlan morton road riding alt tour self supported\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28064144/lachlan-morton-world-bicycle-relief-alt-tour-solo-challenge.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28064144/lachlan-morton-world-bicycle-relief-alt-tour-solo-challenge-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28064144/lachlan-morton-world-bicycle-relief-alt-tour-solo-challenge-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28064144/lachlan-morton-world-bicycle-relief-alt-tour-solo-challenge-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28064144/lachlan-morton-world-bicycle-relief-alt-tour-solo-challenge-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28064144/lachlan-morton-world-bicycle-relief-alt-tour-solo-challenge-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28064144/lachlan-morton-world-bicycle-relief-alt-tour-solo-challenge-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28064144/lachlan-morton-world-bicycle-relief-alt-tour-solo-challenge-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb20 src ng ngcb20 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28064144/lachlan-morton-world-bicycle-relief-alt-tour-solo-challenge.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28064144/lachlan-morton-world-bicycle-relief-alt-tour-solo-challenge.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28064144/lachlan-morton-world-bicycle-relief-alt-tour-solo-challenge-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28064144/lachlan-morton-world-bicycle-relief-alt-tour-solo-challenge-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28064144/lachlan-morton-world-bicycle-relief-alt-tour-solo-challenge-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28064144/lachlan-morton-world-bicycle-relief-alt-tour-solo-challenge-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28064144/lachlan-morton-world-bicycle-relief-alt-tour-solo-challenge-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28064144/lachlan-morton-world-bicycle-relief-alt-tour-solo-challenge-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28064144/lachlan-morton-world-bicycle-relief-alt-tour-solo-challenge-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-263138\">Photo Credit: Grubers</figcaption></figure><p>Those inspired by Lachlan’s challenge and who would like to support him, can donate<br>to <a href=\"https://give.worldbicyclerelief.org/campaign/ef-rapha-for-wbr/c329966\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">World Bicycle Relief</a>. They will use donations to provide even more young people with<br>the bikes they need to access an education. With bikes, travel time is reduced, giving<br>students more time to learn, decreasing student absenteeism by up to 28% (Source: World Bicycle Relief).</p><figure id=\"attachment_263137\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachmen