/en/stories/the-alt-tour\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Dot Watching</a> page hosted by Rapha.</p></div></div>","author":"Jessie-May Morgan","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"b32fb00b2fd7805327205f7f5f7914d50af4542b69016969722faf803ad60301","category":"Cycling"}